1
00:00:06,450 --> 00:00:11,020
=Found & Lost=

2
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:13,940
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,040
Lu Fengtian!

4
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:18,400
Lu Fengtian!

5
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:21,440
Don't shoot!

6
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:23,760
Please don't shoot!

7
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,400
You do the honors.

8
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:31,240
No…

9
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:32,680
I don't want to… No!

10
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:55,560
Don't…

11
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:57,960
Kill me.

12
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,080
Kill me.

13
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,000
It's all my fault.

14
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,200
I'm the cause of all this!

15
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:03,960
Kill me!

16
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,280
Spare him.

17
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:08,200
Let him go.

18
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:09,640
Come at me.

19
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,800
Kill me.

20
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,440
Come on.

21
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,560
Kill me.

22
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,560
Kill me!

23
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,640
I beg you…

24
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,640
Kill me…

25
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,520
My brother

26
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,640
was right.

27
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,280
Tears

28
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,400
and pity

29
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,200
will only lead

30
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:53,000
to one's demise.

31
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:58,760
Zekai,

32
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,240
I can finally join you now.

33
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,120
Huaijin.

34
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,040
Huaijin.

35
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,120
Huaijin!

36
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,240
Come on.

37
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,000
Let's go, Huaijin.

38
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,800
Let's go home.

39
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,680
You're wearing it.

40
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,000
A heart-lock pendant?

41
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:41,240
Wear it, and it means you've agreed.

42
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,640
I put it on.

43
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,000
I'm wearing it.

44
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,520
Huaijin.

45
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,520
Huaijin!

46
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:26,700
♪Born because of you♪

47
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,440
Don't do this.

48
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,680
Don't do this to me…

49
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,640
(My husband,)

50
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,880
(I've come for you.)

51
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,400
Prepare a room in the east wing for her.

52
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,760
Escort her there.

53
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:57,920
That's not necessary.

54
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,480
I can do it myself.

55
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,880
You remind me a lot of someone I know.

56
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,560
Technically, you're still my fiancée.

57
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,640
Clear this away.

58
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,360
She doesn't like sweets.

59
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,240
You are my weakness.

60
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,960
Don't do this to me.

61
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,000
Don't do this to me…

62
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:26,400
Don't do this to me…

63
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:33,420
♪Will surely reach your heart♪

64
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,800
Do what you want to do.

65
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,920
I'll always be behind you.

66
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:59,900
♪Holding you close
at the end of the world♪

67
00:05:00,180 --> 00:05:08,940
♪You are the light
that lingers in my heart♪

68
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:16,580
♪I want us to be together,
night and day♪

69
00:05:16,865 --> 00:05:22,020
♪My words of longing♪

70
00:05:23,540 --> 00:05:28,140
♪Will surely reach your heart♪

71
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,760
(Thus,)

72
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:43,320
(the elders of Haitang Society
and the commander were brought down.)

73
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,800
(The Chinese bloodstone seal
was also donated)

74
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,880
(Shanghai News, Haitang Society)
(to the Red Cross)

75
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,920
(Overthrown, Commander Yang Dies)
(to aid in saving lives.)

76
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,000
(Shanghai News,
Chen Family Orphan Donates Massive Sum)

77
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,840
(And Zhang Mingrui,
who reported all of this,)

78
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:55,440
(A Rising Star in the Journalism World)

79
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:58,240
(finally made a name
for himself in journalism.)

80
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:06,040
Fortune-telling and face reading.

81
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,440
Fortune-telling and face reading.

82
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,080
Miss,

83
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,520
give me a piece

84
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,160
and I'll tell you a story.

85
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,640
20 years ago,

86
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,680
right here,

87
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:39,480
my father was beaten to death
by a group of officers.

88
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:44,880
And after that?

89
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,040
After that, this is all there is.

90
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,180
Out here,
fortune-telling and face reading

91
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,480
for five wen a session.

92
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,280
Did you not go after them?

93
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,690
How can you be all right with that?

94
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,560
Even if I wasn't, what could I do?

95
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,480
I still have a wife,

96
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,360
kids,

97
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,840
and family to look after.

98
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,480
This world is too small

99
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,640
to accommodate

100
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,840
too many sentimental, righteous people.

101
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,160
Give me back my crisp candy.

102
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,360
Miss,

103
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,760
you're still too young.

104
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,400
Take one.

105
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:23,560
Take one.

106
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:37,540
(A dried-up well springs forth water,
most auspicious)

107
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,040
Miss,

108
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,920
cheer up.

109
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:49,720
Duke Zhuang wanders west of the city.

110
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:52,520
Others ride horses, while I ride a mule.

111
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:55,560
From afar, a lone stone rests
on the green mountain.

112
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:58,320
In this world, true gentlemen are few.

113
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,280
A flower-decorated coffin,
finely measured.

114
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:04,200
What does it matter if, in death,
all you have is half a mat?

115
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:07,040
Good and evil eventually reap
what they sow.

116
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:10,400
The true path in life
is full of vicissitudes.

117
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:51,820
(Tomb of Fu Huaijin)

118
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,520
When did your taste change?

119
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,360
I remember
you didn't like sweet things as a kid.

120
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,040
Manli,

121
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,600
you did great.

122
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,000
You're no longer a failure.

123
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,480
Ms. Manli,

124
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,320
you've worked hard.

125
00:10:26,540 --> 00:10:30,060
(Tomb of Fu Huaijin)

126
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,400
Come on.

127
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,040
Let's go home.

128
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,040
(The sunset)

129
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,200
(is beautiful)

130
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,960
(even if you watch it alone.)

131
00:11:49,301 --> 00:12:01,580
(End)

132
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:15,300
♪As dusk approaches, dreams unfold♪

133
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:22,340
♪Laughter drifts with the wind,
hard to hold♪

134
00:12:22,340 --> 00:12:26,220
♪Entwined within the mortal world♪

135
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:29,740
♪Watching fates intertwine, unfurled♪

136
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:36,900
♪Like moths chasing flames,
to blaze they're drawn♪

137
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:41,100
♪We brave the darkness,
spiraling into cocoons♪

138
00:12:41,100 --> 00:12:44,620
♪Chasing a single, unwavering dream♪

139
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:48,380
♪But life's endless twists and turns
can't be undone♪

140
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:52,100
♪As fleeting splendor fades
without regret♪

141
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:55,980
♪We cross the smoke and ashes,
torn by goodbyes♪

142
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:59,300
♪In every moment♪

143
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:03,060
♪Stained by the verses of dawn's light♪

144
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:11,180
♪Love spreads like wildfire,
boundless and bright♪
